---
import { Flame } from '@lucide/astro';
import { Image } from 'astro:assets';
import ProductLimes from '../images/product-limes.webp';
import HeroFire from '../images/hero-fire.webp';
import LifestyleNight from '../images/lifestyle-night.webp';
---

<section class="products" id="sabores">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="section-head reveal">
      <div>
        <span class="eyebrow">03 / Sabores</span>
        <h2>Elige tu<br/><em>temperatura.</em></h2>
      </div>
      <p>Tres botellas. Tres formas de prender el rato. Todas hechas con la misma obsesion por el balance.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="prod-grid">
      <!-- Original -->
      <article class="prod reveal">
        <div class="prod-img">
          <span class="prod-tag hot">Mas vendido</span>
          <Image src={ProductLimes} alt="Pikanté Original" width={1024} height={1536} loading="lazy" />
        </div>
        <div class="prod-body">
          <div class="prod-row1">
            <h3>Original</h3>
            <span class="price" data-v250="L 70 · 250ml" data-v570="L 150 · 570ml" data-v1l="L 260 · 1L">L 150 <span style="color:var(--text-4)">&middot; 570ml</span></span>
          </div>
          <p>El balance clasico: chile de arbol, limon, tamarindo. La puerta de entrada al fuego.</p>
          <div class="prod-variants">
            <button class="variant-pill" data-variant="v250">250ml</button>
            <button class="variant-pill active" data-variant="v570">570ml</button>
            <button class="variant-pill" data-variant="v1l">1 Litro</button>
          </div>
          <div class="prod-row2">
            <span class="chiles" aria-label="Picante 3 de 5">
              <Flame width={16} height={16} fill="currentColor" class='text-(--fire)' />
              <Flame width={16} height={16} fill="currentColor" class='text-(--fire)' />
              <Flame width={16} height={16} fill="currentColor" class='text-(--fire)' />
              <Flame width={16} height={16} fill="currentColor" class='opacity-50 text-(--fire)' />
              <Flame width={16} height={16} fill="currentColor" class='opacity-50 text-(--fire)' />
            </span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </article>
      <!-- Brutal -->
      <!-- <article class="prod reveal" style="transition-delay:.07s">
